'Openshift Local Setup':
This documentation is based on the Openshift Local installation through code-ready container simple Single node installation
System Requirement:

    RHEL8 or RHEL9 Virtual Machine
    Minimum 4 CPU & 12 GB RAM
    32 GB Disk Space in /home
    Virtualization Enabled
    Internet-enabled on VM

1. Install Dependencies:
Install Network Manager, Libvirt, Qemu
